OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777317067
OL,3,CBritish Army takes civilian ferry to
OL,4,CNATO exercise on mainland Europe
OL,6,FThe British Army has used a civilian
OL,7,Fferry to deploy troops to Europe en
OL,8,Fmasse for the first time in a
OL,9,Fgeneration.
OL,11,FMore than 1,400 troops embarked on a
OL,12,FDFDS ferry from North Tyneside on
OL,13,FWednesday (22 April) afternoon for a
OL,14,F16-hour crossing over the North Sea to
OL,15,Fthe Netherlands.
OL,17,FFrom there, the soldiers from the 7th
OL,18,FLight Mechanised Brigade, known as the
OL,19,FDesert Rats, will take trains to
OL,20,Fcentral Germany for NATO's Exercise
OL,21,FRhino Storm.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
