OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777317067
OL,3,CBritish Army takes civilian ferry to
OL,4,CNATO exercise on mainland Europe
OL,6,FThe exercise will demonstrate the
OL,7,FArmy's readiness to respond should
OL,8,FNATO's Article Five be triggered by an
OL,9,Fattack in mainland Europe.
OL,11,FThe Ministry of Defence said using a
OL,12,Fcivilian ferry, usually filled with
OL,13,Florry drivers and trippers to
OL,14,FAmsterdam, was not due to a lack of
OL,15,Fmilitary transport.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777317067
OL,3,CBritish Army takes civilian ferry to
OL,4,CNATO exercise on mainland Europe
OL,6,FCompany Commander Charlie Gilmore of
OL,7,FRight Flank, The Scots Guards, based
OL,8,Fin Catterick, North Yorkshire, said
OL,9,Fusing a civilian ferry for a large-
OL,10,Fscale deployment was "unusual in
OL,11,Frecent times".
OL,13,F"We used them a generation or two ago
OL,14,Fin the Falklands and a generation ago
OL,15,Fin the Gulf conflict," he said.
OL,16,F"There's also a strong reason behind
OL,17,Fit. It shows a kind of flexibility.
OL,26,@rD@VOUsD@MO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777317067
OL,3,CBritish Army takes civilian ferry to
OL,4,CNATO exercise on mainland Europe
OL,6,F"If we were to rely on the strategic
OL,7,Fairlift that's provided by the Royal
OL,8,FAir Force, we would clog all of that
OL,9,Fup to move the circa 1,400 people that
OL,10,Fare going.
OL,12,F"It would take about seven flights to
OL,13,Fdo that. So we can move by air, by
OL,14,Fsea, we can move by rail, and it
OL,15,Fallows us to force-project to the
OL,16,Flocation we need to get to.
OL,18,F"We haven't done it in a while, and we
OL,19,Fneed to practise and rehearse to do
OL,20,Fthat. That's the rationale behind it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777317067
OL,3,CBritish Army takes civilian ferry to
OL,4,CNATO exercise on mainland Europe
OL,6,FThere was no alcohol or duty-free
OL,7,Favailable for the ferry trip which was
OL,8,Freserved for service personnel only.
OL,10,FEntertainment on board included bingo,
OL,11,Fkaraoke and live music.
OL,13,FExercise Rhino Storm will involve live-
OL,14,Ffiring exercises and brigade tactics
OL,15,Fover several weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777317067
OL,3,CBritish Army takes civilian ferry to
OL,4,CNATO exercise on mainland Europe
OL,6,FSecond Lieutenant Ben Claxton, of the
OL,7,F1 Royal Yorkshire Regiment, said: "It
OL,8,Fdemonstrates our ability to move
OL,9,Ftroops from the UK, specifically from
OL,10,Fthe north, to anywhere in Europe, en
OL,11,Fmasse, rapidly, using a variety of
OL,12,Fforms of transport.
OL,14,F"It's a good way to prove we can do it
OL,15,Fand it leaves our airlift and sealift
OL,16,Fcapability free to then bring over
OL,17,Fvehicles and equipment if need be."
OL,26,@oD@cOUvD@AOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
